org.ctoolkit.restapi.client

Interface RestExecutorAdaptee<T,I>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the concrete type of the model object to work with
    I - the concrete type of the resource identifier

    public interface RestExecutorAdaptee<T,I>
    The adaptee interface to provide execute implementation for REST like operations on top of concrete type.
    Author:
    Aurel Medvegy
